name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Antwian MELVIN, Respondent

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Antwian MELVIN, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 9th day of January, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Defendant/Petitioner’s Pro Se Petition for Dismissal/Discharge for Want of Jurisdiction-in the Nature of Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus Ad Subjiciendum ” is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Antwian MELVIN, Respondent.
